results.name: Decimal expansion of 2*sqrt(5)/5 arccsch(2).
comment: Equals the value of the Dirichlet L-series of the non-principal character modulo 5 (A080891) at s=1. - _Jianing Song_, Nov 16 2019
link: R. J. Mathar, Table of Dirichlet L-series.., arXiv:1008.2547, Table 22 for L(m=5,r=3,s=1).
Eric Weisstein's World of Mathematics, Central Binomial Coefficient
formula: Also equals f'(0) = 2*log(phi)/sqrt(5), with f(x) = (phi^x-cos(Pi*x)*phi^-x)/sqrt(5), the real Fibonacci interpolating function. - _Jean-François Alcover_, Apr 04 2014
Equals Sum_{k>=1} F(k)/(k*2^(k+1)), where F(k) is the k-th Fibonacci number (A000045). - _Amiram Eldar_, Aug 10 2020
